About Project:

Project Name: Online Shopping Portal Using C Language.
Author: Yogeshwar Prakash Chaudhari.

////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
//
// Implemented Features:
//
////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////

1) Doubly Linear Linked List
Multiple restaurants and their items are stored using a doubly linear linked list.
Restaurants and items can be added to a .txt file.
Restaurants can also be removed directly from the .txt file (restaurant owner login required).

2) Recursion
Recursion is used to reload the canteen menu dynamically.

3) File Handling
Data is stored in .txt files using file handling.
At runtime, the program fetches and displays this data dynamically.

4) Clear Screen (cls Command)
The system call with the cls command is used to clear the screen for a better user experience.

////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
//
// Other Features:
//
////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////

1) Customer login with personal accounts.
2) Guest login is also supported (without account).
3) View available restaurants.
4) View available items of a specific restaurant.
5) Add items to the cart.
6) Checkout (view selected items, their quantity, price, and GST at 18%).
7) Remove items from the cart.
8) Apply discount coupons.
9) Switch between restaurants (when switching, the cart is cleared automatically).

////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
//
// Future Scope:
